snippet.title: There is Only Power trailer
snippet.description:
"There is Only Power" trailer. This is an evil strategy / roguelike where you attempt to conquer a kingdom before it's citizens can kill you. 

Play it online at http://willswannack.com/thereisonlypower
Download the Mac and Windows versions at http://www.indiedb.com/games/there-is-only-power

Music by Dayazell from Magnatune at http://magnatune.com/artists/albums/dayazell-dayazell?song=1
